{"tid":1877307,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「牛涮鍋」高層自減薪酬抗逆市 稱未有裁減或遣散員工 餐廳曾拒反送中示威者入內","createTime":"2020-02-13T02:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T11:47:12.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f447df2831838108197f180ef7c5c0aa6b6a29d","tid":1877307,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:50:03.000Z","msg":"叙福樓黃傑龍：無員工因短暫休業而裁減或遣散<br />\n<br />\n叙福樓集團(<a href=\"http://01978.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01978.HK&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebcE4f%2F6cKlXs%2FdqEvpC7bjY%3D&h=f3a67935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01978.HK</a>)公布，旗下所有4家「温野菜」及12家「牛涮鍋」餐廳，因應新型肺炎疫情暫停營運，主席及行政總裁黃傑龍及副主席高秀芝下月起暫時減薪一半。<br />\n<br />\n黃傑龍在社交網站帖文指，停業當然對經營帶來困難，但認為共同抗疫明顯比生意經營重要，又指慶幸昨日部分大業主已主動公布減租方案。他又指，堅持沒有一位員工因今次短暫休業決定被裁減或遣散，有關員工將往「牛角」、「牛角次男坊」及「和平飯店」上班，指雖然明顯無足夠崗位，但會盡量想辦法共同面對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1263572&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1263572%26csid%3D261_341&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebcE4f%2F6cKlXs%2FdqEvpC7bjY%3D&h=ebba6a65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1263572&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"d40e5ba0ad70a528c7c6224131a018fed19a6fa6","tid":1877307,"uid":35084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"轉賣其他野啦"},{"pid":"4ffa105427c3b421f66e2cb764e5f89dd5e4aed4","tid":1877307,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:45:05.000Z","msg":"拒入？fc？"},{"pid":"554cf22ec8cafec68cd6c7bf73bea0dacade2204","tid":1877307,"uid":28563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:47:12.000Z","msg":"on9樓主 日牛涮涮鍋 牛涮鍋 兩間分唔清<br />\n係咪冇出過街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被指拒遊行人士入內進餐 日牛涮涮鍋發聲明道歉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352892</a><br /